data.description: Attention Buyers: Rare Find with RV Parking, Storage Shed, and Appx. 5-Minute Access to the Interstate, larger lot!  Step into this irresistible home featuring 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The expansive kitchen is a chef's dream, paired with a cozy living room and an inviting family room. Conveniently, all bedrooms are situated upstairs, adjacent to the utility room for added ease. Plus, indulge in the luxury of RV parking – an extra space for your recreational vehicle. Relish outdoor living on the sprawling concrete patio covered for your enjoyment. Your dream home awaits – act fast!
